  "raw_wikitext": "[[分类:活动剧情]]{{回到顶部|头}}{{面包屑|2025活动剧情|三国志绒绒版/活动玩法}}{{活动背景}}\n\n<div class=\"map-dh\">\n<div class=\"map-dh-left\">三国志绒绒版</div>\n<div class=\"map-dh-right\">\n{{板块|按钮|三国志绒绒版/神谕令·猫邦|神谕令·猫邦对话}}\n{{板块|按钮|三国志绒绒版/神谕令·犬都|神谕令·犬都对话}}\n</div>\n</div>\n{{#css:\n.map-dh {\n    width:100%;\n    overflow:hidden;\n    margin:10px 0px;\n    display:table;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n}\n\n.map-dh-left {\n    display:table-cell;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n    width:140px;\n    padding:10px;\n    font-weight:bold;\n    font-size:16px;\n    background:#7B5F44;\n    color:#F2E3C6;\n    text-align:center;\n}\n\n.map-dh-right {\n    display:table-cell;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n    width:calc(100% - 100px);\n    padding:10px;\n    color:#cbbba4;\n    background:#eee;\n}\n\n.map-dh-an {\n    float: left;\n    width: 120px;\n    color: #848080!important;\n    background: #DCCF9E;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    margin:4px;\n}\n\n.map-dh-an:hover {\n    background:#EAECF0;\n    transition:.2s;\n}\n\n@media only screen and (max-width:759px){\n    .map-dh-an {\n        width:48%;\n        margin:4px 1%;\n    }\n\n    .map-dh-left {\n        display:block;\n        width:100%;\n    }\n\n    .map-dh-right {\n        display:block;\n        width:100%;\n    }\n}\n}}\n{{#css:\n.title{\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 100px;\n    left: 120px;\n    font-size: 4rem;\n    color: #5c0202;\n    }\n    \n @media screen and (max-width: 600px){\n    .chengzhang{\n        width: 120% !important;\n        transform: translateX(-8%);\n    }\n    .title{\n        position: absolute;\n        top: 38px;\n        left: 50px;\n        font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n}\n}}"
